text: <!channel> Podczas najbliższej konferencji <https://infoshare.pl/> odbędzie się warsztat, który może was zainteresować ”Machine Learning: jak obliczyć szanse przeżycia katastrofy na Titanicu?” Warsztat jest prowadzony przez naszych trenerów Marcina Zadrogę i Jakuba Lachowicza. Polecam serdecznie :slightly_smiling_face: <https://infoshare.pl/workshops/>

attachments.title: Infoshare - the biggest tech conference in CEE
attachments.text: Infoshare 2019 - the biggest Tech Conference in CEE (6000+ attendees, 200+ speakers and 500+ startups). Great Networking Party with Live Concert. Take part in this unique experience and join us in Gdansk, Poland, 8-9 May, 2019! Let’s grow with technology!

attachments.text: Workshops are focused on providing attendees with a masterclass on any given topic. You're welcome to attend as many Workshops as you like. 25% discount for all workshops if you have the Conference, Startup, Executive or Investor pass.
